title: JANITORIAL F/T Swing Shift: WATCH Resources is seeking
text:
JANITORIAL F/T Swing Shift: WATCH Resources is seeking ad date: 10/13/2015 
JANITORIAL F/T Swing Shift: WATCH Resources is seeking candidates w/Janitorial exp to supervise/train adults with intellectual disabilities to complete janitorial contracts at a variety of worksites in our community. Comp skills and flex schedule req. $9.27 / hr. + exc. benefits. See website for application/details at watchresources.org or fax resume: 593-2339.
